Additional information for JDK1.3 users

 You have to download some additional jar files (JDK_1.3_Libs.zip):
  http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=21217&release_id=88556

 These jar files are:
  - crimson.jar
  - xalan.jar
  - jaxp.jar

 WINDOWS:
  To run Columba with MS Windows doubleclick the "run_jdk13.bat" file.
  
 LINUX/ UNIX FLAVORS:
  Try the script: "sh run_jdk13.sh"

 OTHERS:
  "java -cp .:ext/csWillySpell.jar:ext/crimson.jar:ext/xalan.jar:ext/jaxp.jar -jar columba.jar"
